    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements for a Class II CPB device. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all 5 operating points. Uncertainty in hemolysis index discussed in narrative; aleatory contributions from blood sample variability and donor fragility differences acknowledged. Assessment team accepts residual uncertainty as consistent with MRL 2 expectations.",
